detaileddescription.para: Some special weights (currently 'weight_obstacle') are repeatedly scaled by this factor in each outer TEB iteration (weight_new = weight_old*factor); Increasing weights iteratively instead of setting a huge value a-priori leads to better numerical conditions of the underlying optimization problem.
